{{冒險遊戲}}
美國電子遊戲公司[[盧卡斯藝術|盧卡斯藝術]]在1986年到2000年期間，發行了共十款以上[[冒險遊戲|冒險遊戲]]作品<ref>{{cite web |url=https://adventuregamers.com/companies/view/812 |title=Adventure games by LucasArts |work=Adventure Games |accessdate=2020-11-22 |archive-date=2021-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120070811/https://adventuregamers.com/companies/view/812 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在被遊戲圈視為是冒險遊戲黃金時期的[[90年代|90年代]]中，有不少盧卡斯藝術冒險遊戲獲得許多來自於遊戲媒體與玩家的好評，以及被《[[有生之年非玩不可的1001款遊戲|有生之年非玩不可的1001款遊戲]]》之類的遊戲工具書籍列為必玩經典<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cbc.ca/arts/a-big-bang-of-creativity-how-lucasarts-brought-cinematic-storytelling-to-video-games-1.4693202 |title=A 'big bang of creativity': How LucasArts brought cinematic storytelling to video games |work= |author=加拿大廣播公司網站 |date=2018-01-05 |accessdate=2020-11-22 |archive-date=2018-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180809154913/https://www.cbc.ca/arts/a-big-bang-of-creativity-how-lucasarts-brought-cinematic-storytelling-to-video-games-1.4693202 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/189899/why_are_we_still_talking_about_.php?print=1 |title=Why are We Still Talking about LucasArts' Old Adventure Games? |work=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] |author=Frank Cifaldi |accessdate=2020-11-22 |archive-date=2014-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140511032819/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/189899/why_are_we_still_talking_about_.php?print=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Fat-ST">{{cite web |url=https://fat-studios.medium.com/the-adventures-of-lucasarts-ceccbf093aba |title=The Adventures of LucasArts |work=Fat-Studio |author=Gavin Annand |accessdate=2020-11-22 |archive-date=2021-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124094636/https://fat-studios.medium.com/the-adventures-of-lucasarts-ceccbf093aba |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.listchallenges.com/1001-video-games-you-must-play-before-you-die/list/6?item=234255 |title=1001 Video Games You Must Play Before You Die - Page 6 |work=List Challenges |accessdate=2020-11-22}}</ref>。這些作品當中也有數款在2000年後獲得[[電子遊戲重製|重製]]機會，以修復成高畫質模樣在遊戲市場上再次出現<ref name="DOTRemastered">{{cite web |url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-10-23-day-of-the-tentacle-remastered-debuts-screenshots |title=Day of the Tentacle Remastered debuts in-game screenshots |work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |author=Jeffrey Matulef |date=2015-10-23 |accessdate=2020-11-22 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108124412/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-10-23-day-of-the-tentacle-remastered-debuts-screenshots |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="FOTRemastered">{{cite web |url=https://www.engadget.com/2017-03-14-full-throttle-remastered-will-tear-up-the-road-this-april.html |title='Full Throttle Remastered' will tear up the road this April |work=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |author=Sean Buckley |date=2017-03-14 |accessdate=2020-11-22 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111210551/https://www.engadget.com/2017-03-14-full-throttle-remastered-will-tear-up-the-road-this-april.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

盧卡斯藝術冒險遊戲當中，多數是透過[[SCUMM|SCUMM]]遊戲引擎製作，在遊戲市場逐漸以[[3D電腦圖形|3D圖形畫面]]作為主流的期間裡，改用了{{tsl|de|GrimE|GrimE}}遊戲引擎<ref name="Gamasutra196009">{{cite web |url=https://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/196009/the_scumm_diary_stories_behind_.php?print=1 |title=The SCUMM Diary: Stories behind one of the greatest game engines ever made |work=Gamasutra |author=Mike Bevan |accessdate=2020-11-22 |archive-date=2019-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616032840/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/196009/the_scumm_diary_stories_behind_.php?print=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.giantbomb.com/grime/3015-1084/ |title=The Grim Engine is the successor to the SCUMM engine for adventure games developed by LucasArts. |work=[[Giant_Bomb|Giant Bomb]] |accessdate=2020-11-22 |archive-date=2019-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191106212021/https://www.giantbomb.com/grime/3015-1084/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在風格上，大多數作品不會有[[玩家角色|玩家角色]]死去造成[[遊戲結束|遊戲結束]]，或是錯過某個步驟造成無法繼續遊戲下去的卡關情況<ref name="stanford">{{cite web |url=https://web.stanford.edu/group/htgg/cgi-bin/drupal/sites/default/files2/cwarren_2003_1.pdf |title=LucasArts and the Design of Successful Adventure Games: The True Secret of Monkey Island |work=[[史丹佛大學|史丹佛大學]] |author=Cameron Warren |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |page=第8、15頁 |date=2003-03-18 |accessdate=2020-11-22 |archive-date=2021-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516060518/https://web.stanford.edu/group/htgg/cgi-bin/drupal/sites/default/files2/cwarren_2003_1.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。遊戲劇情方面，是傾向幽默詼諧的內容居多，並且常暗藏著對母公司[[盧卡斯影業|盧卡斯影業]]發行的《[[星際大戰|星際大戰]]》、《[[印第安納瓊斯系列|印第安納瓊斯]]》等系列影片致意的[[圈內笑話|特別笑點]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://harang.fortunecity.ws/injokes.html |title=Maniac Mansion In-Jokes |work=Fortunecity.WS |author=Jason Harang |date= |accessdate=2020-11-22 |archive-date=2021-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228145930/http://harang.fortunecity.ws/injokes.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://mixnmojo.com/media/galleries/The-Secret-of-Monkey-Island-In-jokes |title=The Secret of Monkey Island (In-jokes) |work=Mixnmojo |accessdate=2020-11-22 |archive-date=2016-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221063338/http://mixnmojo.com/media/galleries/The-Secret-of-Monkey-Island-In-jokes |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在2000年後，盧卡斯藝術開始放棄投入冒險遊戲市場，有不少參與過冒險遊戲開發的盧卡斯藝術人員，離職前往[[訴說遊戲|訴說遊戲]]公司；<ref name="TellTaleGames">{{cite web |url=http://www.telltalegames.com/bio?person=davegrossman |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060516135524/http://www.telltalegames.com/bio?person=davegrossman |dead-url=yes |title=Dave Grossman Senior Designer |work=[[訴說遊戲|訴說遊戲]] |archive-date=2006-05-16 |accessdate=2020-11-22}}</ref>或是自行成立[[Double_Fine_Productions|Double Fine Productions]]、{{tsl|en|Autumn Moon Entertainment|Autumn Moon Entertainment}}等其他公司，繼續投入冒險遊戲的製作<ref name="BusinessInsider">{{cite web |url=https://www.businessinsider.com/tim-schafer-double-fine-interview-2017-3 |title=Legendary game developer Tim Schafer tells us why he's excited for more 'Psychonauts' games, virtual reality, and the new Nintendo Switch |work=Business Insider |author=Dave Smith |date=2017-03-11 |accessdate=2020-11-22 |archive-date=2017-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171026000426/http://www.businessinsider.com/tim-schafer-double-fine-interview-2017-3/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Mixnmojo">{{cite web |url=https://mixnmojo.com/features/interviews/Bill-Tiller-at-Autumn-Moon-Entertainment-2007 |title=Bill Tiller at Autumn Moon Entertainment, 2007 Artist, designer, Master of the Universe |work=Mixnmojo |accessdate=2020-11-22 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304113657/http://mixnmojo.com/features/interviews/Bill-Tiller-at-Autumn-Moon-Entertainment-2007 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

